1.0.name: wordpress/baeblemusic
1.0.description:
Bring video to your Wordpress site in minutes. Baeblemusic provides an entire library of exclusive concerts and session videos, plus thousands of indie and alternative music videos to your site with a simple click.

The Baeblemusic Plugin extends Baeblemusic's entire video library to your site. You can add the plugin as a page or post to easily and immediately include video on your site.

The video plugin allows you to select any or all of the video feeds coming from Baeblemusic. These feeds are:

  • Trending - Updates every 15 minutes with the most watched videos on the platform
  • Newest - Updates throughout the day as we add videos to the platform
  • Concerts - Exclusive long form video from our featured performances of bands and artists that are on the rise, plus acts you already knew
  • Sessions - Exclusive performances from artists in interesting locations. Watch them play a few songs and discuss what
